df <- survey_df[ vnames[ ! vnames %in% id.vars ] ]

non_na_rate <- function(x){ 
  ( 1 - sum( is.na(x)/length(x) ) ) |> round(3)*100 
}

completeness.rate <- sapply( df, non_na_rate )
